706516f-a.title: Brooklyn: Rockaway Parkway - Farragut Road
706516f-a.text:
1319-1341 Rockaway Pkway., near the N.W. corner of Farragut Roai.
In the foreground, is the Rockaway trolley line. In the background, is a rear
view of No. 934-954 East 98th Street.
July 30, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
